Package menuClasses

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Action
    Any object of this type must have a method that executes necessary algorithm to carry-out the action it represents.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddDocumentAction
    This class executes the action of adding a document to the system
    ExitAction
    This class executes the action of exiting the system
    MainMenu
    This class contains the main menu of the system
    Menu
    This class allows the creation of a menu with a given number of options to choose from.
    Option
    Defines the types of options that a menu contains.
    PerformSearchesAction
    This class is used to perform the action of searching in the system
    RemoveDocumentAction
    This class executes the action of removing a document from the system
    RequestInformationAction
    This class executes the action of requesting information about a document in the system
